title: Logitech K360 Wireless Keyboard (Like Apple Wireless Keyboard)
description:
In this video I give a quick tour of the Logitech K360 Wireless Keyboard. This is a great keyboard judging by the price and the features packed into this compact traveling size keyboard. Stay tuned for the review as well as a more in-depth video of the features.
